Company Profile
WANXINDA (GUANGZHOU) TECHNOLOGY PRODUCT CO.,LTD.
Over 22 Years of Manufacturing and Sales Experience
Wanxinda was founded in 1998 in the electronic storage business. Business scope covers the cutting and sewing industry, Injection industry, and testing. With the efforts in the past 22 years, Wanxinda now has factories domestic and overseas that focus on all kinds of bags, luggage, and related accessories, and our goods are suitable for different uses such as school, daily use, outdoor sports & travel, hiking, Digital Gadgets Device Storage and more.
Business Development and New Product Introduction
In 2020 Wanxinda invested almost $15 million to set up the mask production lines in Guangzhou and Hunan factories for Surgical face masks, Medical face masks, and Disposable civilian masks (non-sterile) both for adults & Kids emergently. Wanxinda provides certified quality products to help keep individuals safe and well in times of crisis.
7,000sqm New Factory in Indonesia
To ease the impact of tariffs, Wanxinda invested in an Indonesian factory, PT. Wanxinda Travel Goods established in 2020, with a plant area of more than 7,000 square meters, mainly engaged in computer bags, camera bags, outdoor bags, tool bags, military bags, soft Luggage, and more.
ISO Certified Factory
We have achieved ISO 14064-1:2006, ISO 9001:2008, and ISO 14001:2004 certifications, and we have our own in-house RoHS and REACH testing machines, along with testing labs with temperature and humidity chambers and equipment for color, impact, tensile strength, and drop tests. Our team can also design masks with customer logos upon request.
Contact Us Today
Our products are well-received by clients worldwide including Tesco, Staples, Carrefour, Best Buy, and more. Contact our team now to learn more about our products and services or arrange a site visit.

About us
WANXINDA(GUANGZHOU) TECHNOLOGY PRODUCT CO., LTD
Wanxinda Technology Product Co., Ltd. ( hereinafter referred to as Wanxinda Enterprise ), was found in April 2005, with the registered capital of 150 million Hongkong dollars., covering an area of 100,000 square meters, it is located in Guangzhou Huadu Automobile City Industrial Park with a convenient transportation and beautiful scenery. Wanxinda Enterprise integrates Research and Development, manufacturing and sales, it is now mainly engaged in luggage and protective products (details can be found at www.gsxt.gov.cn). The three subsidiaries provide more than three thousand jobs, pay for taxes and fees about tens of millions Yuan.
Since it's establishment, Wanxinda has always adhered to the business philosophy of "sincerity-based, benefiting the country and the people", and has made unremitting efforts to promote environmental protection and harmonious symbiosis based on corporate development, employee growth and social responsibility. As a private enterprise with the strong sense of responsibility, contribution and mission, Wanxinda Enterprise is closely link it's enterprise development with the social responsibility together and commit to provide consumers with high quality products and a more perfect experience. The company's own brand "WXD" won the " Famous Trademark of Guangdong Province" and " Famous Brand of Guangdong Province", and registered it's trademark in 80 countries and regions including Europe and the United States. It has obtained more than 40 patents for utility models and designs. The product design and manufacturing technology is always at the leading position in the domestic industry.
Over the years, Wanxinda Enterprise has successively won: " Huadu District Private Technology Enterprise", " Huadu District Civilized Enterprise", " Guangzhou A-level Taxpayer", " MBA Practice Research Base of Sun Yat-Sen University Continuing Education College" and " China Leather Leather Manufacturing Technology Upgrade Outstanding Contribution Award" honorary title. passed ISO9001: 2000 international quality management system certification, ISO14001 environmental system certification and ISO14064 carbon neutral certification. In 2010, Wanxinda was awarded the "Guangzhou Cleaner Production Enterprise" and the first Chinese privately-run small and medium-sized enterprise to voluntarily achieve carbon neutrality. In 2012, it was rated as a " Famous Brand of Guangdong Province " and  "Famous Trademark of Guangdong Province". In 2014, it was awarded the title of National High-Tech Enterprise. In 2017, was selected as the designated supplier of bags and luggage for the BRICS leaders, heads of state meeting in Xiamen.Wanxinda Enterprise has always adhered to its position as "The World's Top Manufacturer", to achieve this aim, Wanxinda people have created remarkable achievements one after another. Behind these achievements, it is inseparable from all the people who care about and support the development of Wanxinda. It is precisely because of your trust that Wanxinda can carry out its original aspiration and move forward on the road ahead.
Only by taking a long-term view can we achieve extraordinary results. The existence of the enterprise also shoulders its own mission, not only to seek development for the enterprise, but also to build a platform for employees, create benefits for customers, and contribute to society. These initial missions are also the foundation of Wanxinda's business. One vision and four big missions are condensed into a corporate culture of “Striving for the first and pursuing excellence". Wanxinda is a belief that contains a firm determination to move forward, a spirit of never giving up and the pursuit of lofty ideals. In the future, Wanxinda will still focus on better products and services, provide solutions for users, and protect you in all your travels!
